<td align="center"><b>
<i>Lasioglossum nigroviride</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">&#40;Graenicher, 1911&#41;</font></b><br>
<small><i>Halictus nigro-viridis </i>Graenicher, 1911; <i>Halictus nigroviridis </i>Graenicher, 1911; <i>Dialictus nigroviridis </i>&#40;Graenicher, 1911&#41;; <i>Halictus &#40;Chloralictus&#41; richardsoni </i>Cockerell, 1937; <i>Dialictus richardsoni </i>&#40;Cockerell, 1937&#41;; <i>Lasioglossum &#40;Dialictus&#41; richardsoni </i>&#40;Cockerell, 1937&#41;; <i>Evylaeus pineolensis </i>Mitchell, 1960</small><p>
